  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Grow Your Pets!</h2>This is a fantasy world of chill retro vibes! Here's some key game mechanics:<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Pet Growing System</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/70b85dac81f378da0f8d2b7af83d2eb8.poster.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/70b85dac81f378da0f8d2b7af83d2eb8.webm?t=1701605976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/70b85dac81f378da0f8d2b7af83d2eb8.mp4?t=1701605976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every Pet has 3 stages that affect his appearance. You start with the first stage, and every 25th level Pet will evolve.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Upgrade & Feeding System</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/bc511bae1ef2a3e432d99cc396f55280.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br>Your Pets are alive, so you'll have to feed them! They can be hungry and sad or well-fed and happy.<br>There are 4 stats: strength, stamina, intelligence and luck.<br>You can equip some trinkets and visual modification items on your Pet.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Minigames</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/f6f94ec081e323f805a3447affa2e6de.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br>Fish with your pet - he'll love that!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The Forest</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/422e0c0a5361294c42c54e44775c073a.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br>Get ready to visit the Forest! Who knows, what's waiting for you there..<br><br>And some other features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Crafting & Inventory<br></li><li>Collectables & Stats<br></li><li>Trading system<br></li><li>The primary storyline and daily quests<br></li><li>Day & night cycle (and raining, of course!)<br></li><li>And much more!</li></ul><br><strong>We wish you to have a good time!</strong>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Welcome to Grow Your Pets!</h2>This is a fantasy world of chill retro vibes! Here's some key game mechanics:<br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Pet Growing System</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/70b85dac81f378da0f8d2b7af83d2eb8.poster.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/70b85dac81f378da0f8d2b7af83d2eb8.webm?t=1701605976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/70b85dac81f378da0f8d2b7af83d2eb8.mp4?t=1701605976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Every Pet has 3 stages that affect his appearance. You start with the first stage, and every 25th level Pet will evolve.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Upgrade & Feeding System</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/bc511bae1ef2a3e432d99cc396f55280.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br>Your Pets are alive, so you'll have to feed them! They can be hungry and sad or well-fed and happy.<br>There are 4 stats: strength, stamina, intelligence and luck.<br>You can equip some trinkets and visual modification items on your Pet.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Minigames</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/f6f94ec081e323f805a3447affa2e6de.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br>Fish with your pet - he'll love that!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>The Forest</strong></li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2253770/extras/422e0c0a5361294c42c54e44775c073a.avif?t=1701605976\" width=616 height=270 /></span><br>Get ready to visit the Forest! Who knows, what's waiting for you there..<br><br>And some other features:<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Crafting & Inventory<br></li><li>Collectables & Stats<br></li><li>Trading system<br></li><li>The primary storyline and daily quests<br></li><li>Day & night cycle (and raining, of course!)<br></li><li>And much more!</li></ul><br><strong>We wish you to have a good time!</strong>",
